1425
01:22:08.156 --> 01:22:11.946
A lot of times, it's thought that the PT3 mutation occurs before the BRCA loss of

1426
01:22:11.956 --> 01:22:15.506
heterozygosity, and so it's perhaps that line one dysregulation occurs before

1427
01:22:15.576 --> 01:22:19.136
that. And certainly, in patients who are inheriting PT3 mutations, I think that's a

1428
01:22:19.216 --> 01:22:22.946
strong possibility. So I think that everything that we're learning,

1429
01:22:23.276 --> 01:22:26.736
things from these autoantibody studies, things from line one studies, are also

1430
01:22:26.756 --> 01:22:29.696
going to help us understand how these cancers are developing in these patients.

